description:
Introducing the **2020 Toyota Corolla XSE** featuring the **All-Weather Floor Liner Package**‚Äîa smart choice for drivers seeking a harmonious blend of efficiency, technology, and safety. This certified vehicle is powered by a robust Dynamic Force 2L I-4 engine, delivering an impressive 169 horsepower. Coupled with a smooth 10-speed automatic/CVT transmission, the Corolla XSE ensures an optimal balance of performance and fuel economy.

One of the standout features of the Corolla XSE is its smart device mirroring capability. This innovative feature allows seamless integration of your smartphone with the vehicle‚Äôs infotainment system, enabling you to access essential apps while keeping your focus on the road. This functionality enhances both convenience and safety, making your driving experience more enjoyable.

Safety is a top priority in the Corolla XSE, with advanced systems like forward collision mitigation. This technology continuously monitors the road ahead and prepares the vehicle for potential collisions, significantly reducing the risk of accidents. Additionally, the front pedestrian impact prevention system actively scans for pedestrians, ensuring you stay safe in urban environments.

The rear camera further enhances safety by providing a clear view of obstacles behind the vehicle, making parking and reversing much easier. Lane departure prevention technology helps maintain your vehicles position within its lane, automatically correcting any unintended drift. Moreover, the adaptive cruise control with traffic stop-go feature allows you to maintain a safe distance from the vehicle ahead, making long drives less stressful and more pleasurable.

Comfort is not overlooked in the Corolla XSE. The heated driver and front passenger seats provide quick warmth during cold weather, ensuring a cozy ride. The mobile hotspot capability turns your vehicle into a Wi-Fi hub, keeping you and your passengers connected on the go without tapping into your phones data plan.

In summary, the **2020 Toyota Corolla XSE** with the **All-Weather Floor Liner Package** stands out as a remarkable compact sedan that excels in safety, technology, and comfort. With its powerful engine and cutting-edge features, the Corolla XSE is designed to meet the needs of modern drivers. Experience the perfect blend of functionality and style and redefine your driving journey today!

Boasting a sleek Celestite exterior and a spacious, well-appointed interior, this Corolla XLE is a true head-turner. The 1.8L I4 DOHC 16V engine, paired with a smooth-shifting CVT transmission, delivers an exceptional blend of power and efficiency, with an impressive 29 city/37 highway MPG rating.

Step inside and experience the unparalleled comfort of the heated front bucket seats, wrapped in premium SofTex leather trim. The power driver's seat and tilt/telescoping steering wheel ensure a perfect driving position, while the intuitive infotainment system, featuring a state-of-the-art navigation system, keeps you connected and entertained on every journey.

Safety is paramount in the Corolla XLE, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including the Rear Parking Camera, Auto High-beam Headlights, and the Safety Connect emergency communication system.   • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

  • This \'intelligent\' cruise control system uses laser or radar to maintain a preset following distance behind another vehicle, automatically braking (to a complete stop if needed) or accelerating as required.
Safety and Security
  • The vehicle is equipped with a system that senses, and then prepares, the vehicle and/or occupants, for an impending forward collision.
  • The vehicle constantly monitors the roadway in front of the vehicle and identifies and tracks pedestrians on an interior display. If the system determines a likely impact, it will automatically take preventative steps to avoid hitting the pedestrian.
  • The vehicle is equipped with a camera that displays an image of the area behind the vehicle on an interior display.
  • An active lane departure system alerts the driver of unintended movement of the vehicle out of a designated traffic lane and automatically maintains the vehicle's position within that lane.
  • Brake assist senses panic braking from the speed of the brake pedal's travel and applies all available power brake boost.
Technology and Telematics
  • Without the need for a manufacturer specific app to be installed on the smart device, the vehicle infotainment system can access and control functions of a smart device physically plugged-into the vehicle.

description:
Discover the pinnacle of luxury and performance in this stunning 2020 Cadillac CT6 3.6L Luxury. Boasting a sleek Stellar Black Metallic exterior and a meticulously crafted Black interior, this exceptional vehicle is the embodiment of Cadillac's relentless pursuit of excellence.

Packed with an impressive array of features, this CT6 Luxury model stands out from the crowd. Key highlights include:

‚Ä¢ Stellar Black Metallic exterior
‚Ä¢ Black interior
‚Ä¢ Preferred Equipment Group 1SB
‚Ä¢ Radio: Cadillac User Experience with Embedded Navigation

Beyond these standout features, the CT6 Luxury is equipped with a host of premium amenities that elevate the driving experience. Enjoy the convenience of the Navigation System, the entertainment of SiriusXM Radio, and the comfort of Automatic Temperature Control and Front Dual Zone A/C. The Power Moonroof and Exterior Parking Camera Rear add to the vehicle's versatility, while the Heated Driver and Front Passenger Seats and Leather Seating Surfaces provide unparalleled comfort.

Powered by a 3.6L V6 SIDI DOHC VVT engine mated to a 10-Speed Automatic transmission and All-Wheel Drive, this CT6 Luxury delivers exceptional performance and handling. With an EPA-estimated 18 MPG in the city and 27 MPG on the highway, you can enjoy the thrill of the drive while maintaining impressive fuel efficiency.

Cadillac's commitment to safety is evident in the CT6 Luxury, which boasts a suite of advanced features, including Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, Knee Airbag, Overhead Airbag, and Electronic Stability Control. These cutting-edge technologies work in harmony to provide you and your loved ones with the utmost protection on the road.

Experience the pinnacle of luxury, performance, and safety in this remarkable 2020 Cadillac CT6 3.6L Luxury. We invite you to schedule a test drive and discover the unparalleled driving experience that awaits you. Contact us today to make this exceptional vehicle your own.

  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

The intuitive Lexus Premium Sound System with 10 speakers will immerse you in a concert-like audio experience, while the Electrochromic Rear-View Mirror and Auto-dimming Door Mirrors provide enhanced visibility and convenience.

description:
Check out this 2020 Honda Civic Si Sedan Manual w/Summer Tires finished in Rallye Red with a Black interior. This vehicle is equipped with the following features and options: Convenience
  • Distance pacing cruise control - Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with Distance pacing cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and the vehicle ahead. Distance pacing cruise control, your ultimate co-pilot.
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

This stunning 2020 Lexus IS 350 is a true standout in its class, boasting a remarkable combination of style, performance, and advanced features. With its sleek exterior, powerful 3.5L V6 engine, and an impressive array of premium amenities, this IS 350 is the epitome of luxury and sophistication.

‚Ä¢ Accessory Package
‚Ä¢ F SPORT Package
‚Ä¢ Navigation Package
‚Ä¢ 10 Speakers
‚Ä¢ AM/FM Radio
‚Ä¢ CD player
‚Ä¢ Intuitive Park Assist
‚Ä¢ Auto High-beam Headlights
‚Ä¢ Heated & Ventilated Front F SPORT Seats
‚Ä¢ Lexus Enform App Suite (Subscription Free)
‚Ä¢ LFA Inspired TFT Instrumentation
‚Ä¢ F SPORT NuLuxe Seat Trim
‚Ä¢ Alloy Wheels

Slip behind the wheel of this exceptional Lexus and experience the thrill of its responsive handling and smooth, effortless acceleration. The 8-speed automatic transmission with Direct Shift delivers seamless power delivery, while the Torsen Limited-Slip Differential ensures confident traction and control, even in challenging conditions.

The interior of the IS 350 is a true sanctuary of luxury, with premium materials and thoughtful design elements that cater to your every need. The F SPORT-tuned Adaptive Variable Suspension (AVS) and unique front fascia/grille add a touch of sporty flair, while the heated and ventilated front seats keep you comfortable in any weather.

Cutting-edge technology is at your fingertips, with features like the Lexus Enform Destinations, Lexus Insider, and the intuitive Remote Touch interface. The 10-speaker audio system and SiriusXM radio ensure an immersive listening experience, while the rearview camera and Intuitive Park Assist make maneuvering a breeze.

Safety is also a top priority in the IS 350, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver assistance technologies, including Lexus Enform Safety Connect, ABS brakes, and a host of airbags to protect you and your passengers.

Discover the exceptional craftsmanship and uncompromising performance of this 2020 Lexus IS 350. Experience the difference that true luxury can make in your daily driving. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why this remarkable vehicle should be your next automotive companion.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2020 Toyota Avalon Hybrid Limited. This sophisticated and eco-friendly sedan offers a captivating blend of advanced technology, uncompromising comfort, and exceptional fuel efficiency.

Boasting an impressive array of premium features, this Avalon Hybrid Limited is tailored to exceed your expectations. Key highlights include:

‚Ä¢ Navigation System
‚Ä¢ 14-Speaker Premium Audio System
‚Ä¢ Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control
‚Ä¢ Heads-Up Display
‚Ä¢ Power Moonroof
‚Ä¢ Heated and Ventilated Front Seats
‚Ä¢ Heated Rear Seats
‚Ä¢ Genuine Wood Trim
‚Ä¢ Heated Steering Wheel

Powered by a state-of-the-art I4 Continuously Variable Transmission (ECVT) powertrain, this Avalon Hybrid delivers an exceptional 43 MPG in the city and on the highway, making it an ideal choice for the eco-conscious driver. The advanced hybrid system seamlessly combines electric and gasoline power, ensuring a smooth and responsive driving experience while minimizing your carbon footprint.

Beyond its impressive performance, the Avalon Hybrid Limited exudes an elegant and refined presence. The striking exterior design, with its sleek lines and distinctive styling cues, commands attention on the road. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a meticulously crafted cabin that pampers you with premium materials, thoughtful ergonomics, and a host of cutting-edge technologies.

Safety is also a top priority, with the Avalon Hybrid Limited boasting a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance features. From the Rear Camera to the Emergency Communication System, you can drive with confidence, knowing you and your loved ones are well-protected.

If you're seeking a luxurious and eco-friendly sedan that seamlessly blends performance, technology, and style, this 2020 Toyota Avalon Hybrid Limited is an exceptional choice. We invite you to experience its remarkable capabilities firsthand. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and discover the joy of driving this exceptional vehicle.

description:
**HONDA CERTIFIED** Thank you for choosing Classic Honda, this Platinum White Pearl 2020 Honda Accord Sedan LX is a great choice! Check out the following: Safety and Security
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
  • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.

Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and technology in this stunning 2020 BMW 2 Series 228i Gran Coupe xDrive. This exceptional vehicle offers an unparalleled driving experience, with its potent 2.0L 4-Cylinder engine and 8-Speed Automatic Sport transmission delivering impressive power and efficiency. Equipped with BMW's renowned all-wheel-drive system, the 2 Series 228i Gran Coupe xDrive provides confident handling and exceptional traction, ensuring a thrilling and secure ride in any conditions.

Boasting a sleek Gray exterior and a well-appointed interior, this 2 Series is a true head-turner. Key features include:

‚Ä¢ Limited 6 month or 6000 mile Warranty
‚Ä¢ Comfort Access Keyless Entry
‚Ä¢ Panoramic Moonroof
‚Ä¢ SiriusXM Satellite Radio with 1 year All Access subscription
‚Ä¢ 18" Bi-Color Multi-Spoke Wheels
‚Ä¢ Heated Front Seats and Steering Wheel

The comprehensive Convenience Package elevates your driving experience with thoughtful amenities, while the premium sound system and advanced connectivity options keep you entertained and connected on the go. With a focus on both style and substance, this 2 Series 228i Gran Coupe xDrive is a true standout in its class.

Beneath the striking exterior lies a wealth of advanced safety and driver-assistance technologies, including Blind Spot Monitoring, Lane Departure Warning, Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, and a Backup Camera. These cutting-edge features work in harmony to help keep you and your passengers secure on the road.

Boasting an impressive EPA-estimated 23 MPG in the city and 33 MPG on the highway, this 2 Series 228i Gran Coupe xDrive delivers exceptional fuel efficiency without compromising on performance. Whether you're commuting or embarking on a weekend getaway, this BMW will get you there in style and comfort.

This 2020 BMW 2 Series 228i Gran Coupe xDrive is a true gem, offering a captivating blend of style, technology, and driving dynamics. With its limited warranty, comprehensive features, and impressive efficiency, this vehicle is an exceptional value that shouldn't be missed. Visit our showroom today to experience the thrill of owning this remarkable BMW for yourself.

Discover the exceptional 2020 Honda Accord Sport, a sophisticated and dynamic sedan that seamlessly blends style, performance, and cutting-edge technology. This meticulously maintained Accord Sport, with its sleek white exterior, embodies the perfect balance of elegance and athleticism.

Powered by a spirited 1.5-liter turbocharged engine, the Accord Sport delivers an exhilarating driving experience, with an impressive 29 city and 35 highway MPG. Its responsive CVT transmission and front-wheel-drive layout provide a smooth, agile, and confident ride, whether navigating city streets or cruising down the highway.

Beyond its dynamic capabilities, the Accord Sport pampers you with a wealth of premium features. The sleek, modern interior is adorned with high-quality materials, including a leather-wrapped steering wheel and shift knob. Seamless smartphone integration via Apple CarPlay and Android Auto keeps you connected and entertained on the go.

Safety is also a top priority, with the Accord Sport's suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including Collision Mitigation Braking System, Lane Departure Warning, and Adaptive Cruise Control, providing you and your loved ones with added peace of mind.

As a family-owned and operated dealership serving the Sarasota community for over 30 years, we take pride in offering exceptional vehicles and unparalleled customer service. Our CARFAX Top-Rated Lifetime Dealer status is a testament to our commitment to transparency and customer satisfaction.

Experience the exceptional 2020 Honda Accord Sport for yourself. Call, email, or chat with us today to schedule a personalized video walkthrough or an exhilarating test drive. We're confident this Accord Sport will exceed your expectations and become the perfect addition to your driving lifestyle.

Fort Myers Genesis-Volvo Cars is committed to 100% customer satisfaction, no exceptions. We are honored at the opportunity to earn your business. Welcome to Fort Myers Genesis-Volvo Cars. Welcome to Fort Myers Genesis-Volvo Cars. Our team strives to make your next vehicle purchase hassle free.

Vehicle Details
Discover refined luxury and performance with this 2020 Genesis G80 3.8L AWD, now available in Fort Myers, FL. With only 27,996 miles, this low-mileage executive sedan combines a smooth V6 3.8L gasoline engine and all-wheel drive for confident handling in any season. Impeccably maintained and feature-rich, the Genesis G80 delivers premium comfort and modern technology at the best price in the area.

Inside, enjoy seamless connectivity with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto alongside an integrated Navigation system for effortless travel planning. Automatic Climate Control keeps the cabin perfectly comfortable while advanced safety features such as Lane Keep Assist enhance driver confidence on long commutes and highway drives. The well-appointed interior offers upscale materials and a thoughtful layout designed for relaxation and convenience.

This Genesis G80 balances performance, safety, and technology‚Äîmaking it an excellent choice for buyers seeking a near-luxury experience without the new-car price. Low mileage and meticulous upkeep contribute to long-term value and reliability. Located in Fort Myers, FL, this vehicle is priced competitively to sell quickly. Schedule a test drive today to experience the refined ride, outstanding features, and exceptional value of this 2020 Genesis G80 3.8L AWD before it's gone.

Equipment
This unit has auto-adjust speed for safe following. It is equipped with all wheel drive. This model offers Android Auto for seamless smartphone integration. Apple CarPlay: Seamless smartphone integration for this unit - stay connected and entertained on the go! This 2020 Genesis G80 offers Automatic Climate Control for personalized comfort. See what's behind you with the back up camera on the Genesis G80. This vehicle is a certified CARFAX 1-owner. Maintaining a stable interior temperature in this Genesis G80 is easy with the climate control system. This 2020 Genesis G80 features cruise control for long trips. Electronic Stability Control is one of many advanced safety features on the vehicle. The vehicle has a V6, 3.8L high output engine. This unit is equipped with a gasoline engine. Bluetooth technology is built into this model, keeping your hands on the steering wheel and your focus on the road. Lane Keep Assist in the vehicle helps maintain safe driving by gently steering to stay within the lane. This is one of the largest cars available. The leather seats in this model are a must for buyers looking for comfort, durability, and style. With the adjustable lumbar support in this 2020 Genesis G80 your back will love you. The installed navigation system will keep you on the right path. Start this 2020 Genesis G80 from inside with remote start. This Genesis G80 shines with clean polished lines coated with an elegant white finish. Night driving with HID Xenon headlamps is a breeze in this large car.

Key features of this 2020 Toyota Camry LE include:
‚Ä¢ Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
‚Ä¢ 7.5J x 17" Alloy Wheels

This Camry LE is the perfect blend of style, comfort, and technology. With its sleek black exterior and well-appointed interior, it's sure to turn heads wherever you go. Under the hood, you'll find a 2.5L I4 DOHC 16V engine mated to an 8-Speed Automatic transmission, delivering an impressive 28 city/39 highway MPG.

Settle into the comfortable fabric seats and enjoy the convenience of features like power windows, power door locks, and steering wheel-mounted audio controls. Stay connected with the AM/FM audio system and enjoy the added benefit of SiriusXM radio. This model is powered by a robust 2L I-4 DOHC engine with 158 horsepower, paired with a smooth CVT transmission, ensuring a thrilling driving experience while maintaining excellent fuel economy.One of the standout features of the Honda Civic Sport is its **Smart Device Mirroring** capability, allowing you to seamlessly connect your smartphone with the vehicles infotainment system. This feature enhances convenience and safety, as it enables you to control your device without taking your eyes off the road.Safety is paramount, and the Civic Sport excels with its **Forward Collision Mitigation** system. This proactive technology detects potential collisions and prepares the vehicle to minimize impact, ensuring peace of mind during your commutes. Additionally, the **Front Pedestrian Impact Prevention** feature offers an extra layer of safety, constantly monitoring the road for pedestrians and taking action to avoid accidents.The **Rear Camera** provides enhanced visibility, making reversing easier and safer by displaying a clear image of obstacles behind the vehicle. Coupled with **Lane Departure Prevention**, this model helps keep you in your lane by automatically correcting any unintentional drift, promoting safer driving habits.For those long road trips, the **Adaptive Cruise Control with Traffic Stop-Go** feature is a game changer. This system maintains your desired speed and automatically adjusts to keep a safe distance from the vehicle ahead, even stopping and starting as traffic dictates, making highway driving more relaxed.The **Brake Assist** feature ensures that in emergency situations, your stopping power is maximized when needed most. Additionally, **Cruise Control with Steering Wheel Mounted Controls** makes it easy to set your speed for a more comfortable drive, reducing fatigue during longer journeys.For added convenience, the **Keyfob Vehicle Start Control** allows you to start your engine remotely, ensuring your vehicle is ready to go when you are. The **Touchscreen** interface further enhances usability, allowing you to control various features with just a touch.In conclusion, the **Certified 2020 Honda Civic Sport** is not just about performance, it‚Äôs about providing a safe, comfortable, and technologically advanced driving experience. Take command of every road in the 2021 Nissan Titan 5.6L Endurance V8 SV, finished in sleek Gun Metallic Gray. This powerful full-size truck combines rugged performance with modern design, offering a bold presence and the capability to handle any challenge, on-road or off.

Step inside to enjoy heated captain's chairs for ultimate comfort, remote engine start for convenience, and traffic sign recognition to stay informed and safe on every drive. The cabin is thoughtfully designed to keep you connected and comfortable while providing the toughness you expect from a Titan.

Equipped with the Off-Road Protection Package, this truck is ready for dirt, rocks, and trails with added durability and confidence. From worksite demands to weekend adventures, the 2021 Titan Endurance V8 SV delivers performance, comfort, and reliability in every mile.

Proudly serving Grand Prairie, Dallas, Fort Worth, Arlington, Midlothian, Cedar Hill, Mansfield and all of DFW and North Texas.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of efficiency and style with the 2025 Hyundai Elantra Hybrid Blue. This meticulously maintained hybrid sedan boasts an impressive array of features that cater to your driving needs and elevate your daily commute.

Highlighted by its exceptional fuel economy, the Elantra Hybrid delivers an unparalleled 51 MPG in the city and an astounding 58 MPG on the highway, making it an exceptional choice for the eco-conscious driver. Complementing its efficient performance, this vehicle is equipped with:

‚Ä¢ CARPETED FLOOR MATS
‚Ä¢ ALLOY DOOR SILLS
‚Ä¢ CARGO NET
‚Ä¢ FIRST AID KIT

Hyundai's commitment to quality and innovation shines through in the Elantra Hybrid. This certified pre-owned vehicle has undergone a rigorous 173-point inspection, ensuring that it meets the highest standards of safety and reliability. With a Limited Warranty covering 60 months or 60,000 miles, and a Powertrain Limited Warranty extending to 120 months or 100,000 miles, you can drive with confidence, knowing your investment is protected.

The Elantra Hybrid's sleek and modern exterior, complemented by its Gray color, exudes a sense of sophistication and style. Under the hood, the efficient I4 engine paired with a 6-Speed Dual Clutch transmission delivers a responsive and engaging driving experience, while the Front-Wheel Drive system provides confident handling in various road conditions.

Step inside the Elantra Hybrid and discover a cabin that seamlessly blends comfort and technology. Enjoy the convenience of automatic temperature control, remote keyless entry, and a state-of-the-art infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration. The premium cloth seating and driver-focused ergonomics create an environment that is both inviting and practical.

Safety is paramount in the Elantra Hybrid, which is equipped with an array of advanced driver-assistance features. From the Rear Camera to the Blind Spot Monitoring system, you can navigate the roads with confidence, knowing that you and your passengers are well-protected.

This exceptional Hyundai Elantra Hybrid Blue is a testament to the brand's commitment to delivering exceptional value, performance, and sustainability. With its unbeatable fuel efficiency, comprehensive warranty coverage, and impressive list of features, this vehicle is the perfect choice for the discerning driver who demands excellence. Schedule a test drive today and experience the future of hybrid driving.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this stunning 2025 Honda Accord SE. This meticulously maintained sedan boasts a sleek black exterior and a host of premium features that will captivate your senses and elevate your daily commute.

‚Ä¢ Blind Spot Information (BSI) System warning
‚Ä¢ Lane Keeping Assist System (LKAS) active
‚Ä¢ Adaptive Cruise Control (ACC) with Low-Speed Follow
‚Ä¢ Power moonroof
‚Ä¢ 180-Watt Audio System
‚Ä¢ Exterior Parking Camera Rear

Designed with your comfort and convenience in mind, this Accord SE offers an impressive array of amenities. Enjoy the seamless integration of Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, allowing you to stay connected on the go. The dual-zone automatic climate control ensures a personalized driving environment, while the heated front seats provide warmth on chilly days. The powerful 1.5-liter turbocharged engine, paired with a continuously variable transmission, delivers an exceptional balance of performance and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 29 MPG in the city and 37 MPG on the highway.

Safety is of paramount importance, and this Accord SE is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features. The Blind Spot Information System and Lane Keeping Assist System work in tandem to enhance your awareness and provide an extra layer of protection. The Adaptive Cruise Control with Low-Speed Follow takes the stress out of highway driving, automatically adjusting your speed to maintain a safe following distance.

Elevate your driving experience with the perfect blend of style, technology, and performance. This 2025 Honda Accord SE is a true testament to Honda's commitment to excellence. Schedule a test drive today and discover the joy of owning this exceptional vehicle.

At our dealership, we are dedicated to providing our customers with an exceptional buying experience. Our knowledgeable sales team is here to assist you every step of the way, ensuring that you find the perfect vehicle to meet your needs and exceed your expectations. We take pride in our commitment to customer satisfaction, and we look forward to the opportunity to earn your business.

Don't miss your chance to own this remarkable 2025 Honda Accord SE. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and experience the difference for yourself. We're confident that once you get behind the wheel, you'll be captivated by the unparalleled combination of style, technology, and performance that this vehicle has to offer.

This Toyota Camry LE delivers an exceptional driving experience with its 2.5L 4-cylinder engine and eCVT transmission, providing a smooth and efficient ride. Boasting an impressive 53 MPG in the city and 50 MPG on the highway, this Camry will keep you on the road longer between fill-ups, saving you time and money.

Elevate your daily commute or weekend adventures with the Camry's comprehensive suite of safety features, including Automatic High Beams, Blind Spot Monitoring, and Toyota Safety Sense. You can drive with confidence, knowing this vehicle has your back.

As a Toyota Gold Certified pre-owned vehicle, this Camry has undergone a rigorous 160-point inspection and comes with a comprehensive warranty package. Enjoy the peace of mind of a 12-month/12,000-mile limited comprehensive warranty, an 84-month/100,000-mile powertrain warranty, and 7 years/100,000 miles of roadside assistance. This Camry is ready to provide you with years of reliable and worry-free ownership.

With its sleek black exterior, the 2025 Toyota Camry LE is sure to turn heads wherever you go. The 16-inch alloy wheels and body-colored bumpers add a touch of sophistication, while the interior's fabric seat trim and split-folding rear seat provide both comfort and versatility.

Don't miss your opportunity to own this exceptional 2025 Toyota Camry LE. Visit our showroom today and experience the quality, efficiency, and peace of mind that come with this certified pre-owned Toyota. We're confident you'll be impressed by this Camry's exceptional value and performance.

Why BUY from Bill Jacobs Volkswagen? When you choose this Platinum Gray Metallic 2025 Volkswagen Jetta SE with 6,112 miles, you are not just buying a used vehicle - you are investing in quality, reliability and peace of mind. Our clientele depend on us for Transparent Pricing, Convenience and, most importantly, Customer FIRST Service! No Accidents! One Owner! What this vehicle includes: Convenience
  • Unresponsive driver assistant - a reaction to inaction. Maybe you fell asleep. Maybe you lost consciousness. No matter how it happens, Unresponsive driver assistant works to help lessen the danger when it does. It detects prolonged driver unresponsiveness, automatically bringing the vehicle to a stop and turning on the hazard lights. If equipped, emergency services will also be contacted. Unresponsive driver assistant is safety that never sleeps.
Safety and Security
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
Technology and Telematics
  • Wireless App-Connect (w/Apple CarPlay, Android Auto & MirrorLink) smart device wireless mirroring
PLATINUM GRAY METALLIC, GRIGIO/TITAN BLACK, CLOUDTEX & V-TEX LEATHERETTE SEAT TRIM Come on in to Bill Jacobs Volkswagen today at 2211 Aurora Ave Naperville IL 60540 or call 844-746-7928 to schedule a test drive!

The Napleton Auto Group promotes a no pressure buying experience that puts the customer in charge of the buying process, and for over 80 years, the Napleton family has made sure that absolutely nothing is more important than our commitment to your satisfaction. Our staff members are professional in every sense of the word, and receive regular training, including factory certification, so they are truly knowledgeable about the vehicles we offer. We want every customer's experience to be as timely, comfortable and ultimately as satisfying as it possible can be. You'll see it in every department of every Napleton Auto Group dealership. We hope you'll join the thousands of other satisfied customers that buy and service their vehicles the Napleton way. No Accidents! One Owner! This 2025 Hyundai Elantra SE offered in Intense Blue will make a great addition to your family or business! Be sure to take note of all this vehicle has to offer: Option Group 01
    Convenience
    • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
    Safety and Security
    • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
    • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
    • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Apple CarPlay & Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
    Other notable features: Napleton Downtown Chevrolet Buick GMC is proud to serve customers in communities throughout the Chicagoland area. description:
Why BUY from Bill Jacobs Volkswagen? When you choose this Pyrite Silver Metallic 2025 Volkswagen Jetta SE with 7,517 miles, you are not just buying a used vehicle - you are investing in quality, reliability and peace of mind. Our clientele depend on us for Transparent Pricing, Convenience and, most importantly, Customer FIRST Service! No Accidents! One Owner! What this vehicle includes: Convenience
  • Unresponsive driver assistant - a reaction to inaction. Maybe you fell asleep. Maybe you lost consciousness. No matter how it happens, Unresponsive driver assistant works to help lessen the danger when it does. It detects prolonged driver unresponsiveness, automatically bringing the vehicle to a stop and turning on the hazard lights. If equipped, emergency services will also be contacted. Unresponsive driver assistant is safety that never sleeps.
Safety and Security
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
Technology and Telematics
  • Wireless App-Connect (w/Apple CarPlay, Android Auto & MirrorLink) smart device wireless mirroring

Volkswagen works hard for your safety, supplying automatic braking, adaptive cruise control, a rearview camera, blind-spot monitoring, forward collision warning, and more. This 2025 Mazda Mazda3 2.5 S Preferred Package is a standout choice for the discerning driver. Boasting a sleek Soul Red Crystal Metallic exterior, this meticulously maintained vehicle offers a compelling blend of style, performance, and advanced technology.

Key features include:
‚Ä¢ SOUL RED CRYSTAL METALLIC PAINT CHARGE
‚Ä¢ HIGH WALL ALL-WEATHER FLOOR MATS
‚Ä¢ CARGO TRAY

Beneath the hood, the 2.5L I4 DOHC 16V LEV3-SULEV30 engine delivers an impressive 191 horsepower, paired with a smooth-shifting 6-Speed Automatic transmission and front-wheel drive. This powertrain not only provides a responsive and engaging driving experience but also achieves an exceptional fuel efficiency of 27 mpg in the city and 37 mpg on the highway.

The Mazda3's interior is equally impressive, with a wealth of premium features that cater to your every need. Enjoy the comfort of heated front seats, the convenience of a power driver's seat, and the seamless integration of the MAZDA CONNECT Infotainment System, complete with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto compatibility. The panoramic moonroof adds an extra touch of elegance, while the comprehensive suite of advanced safety technologies, including Blind Spot Monitoring, Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, and Adaptive Cruise Control, provide added peace of mind on the road.

With its sleek styling, impressive performance, and impressive array of features, this 2025 Mazda Mazda3 2.5 S Preferred Package is a truly exceptional value. We invite you to experience the difference for yourself by scheduling a test drive at our showroom. Our knowledgeable sales team is ready to answer any questions you may have and guide you through the buying process, ensuring a seamless and enjoyable experience.

Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this exceptional Mazda Certified Pre-Owned vehicle. Contact us today to learn more and take the first step towards driving home in your dream car.

Drive into the New Year at Collierville Chrysler Dodge Jeep Ram.

This 2025 Toyota Camry SE is a standout in its class, boasting a remarkable suite of features that elevate your driving experience. Highlighted by a powerful 2.5L 4-cylinder engine, this Camry SE delivers an exceptional 48 city/47 highway MPG, ensuring exceptional fuel efficiency and cost savings.

‚Ä¢ Power Tilt/Slide Moonroof
‚Ä¢ Multimedia Upgrade Package with 12.3" Touchscreen
‚Ä¢ Convenience Package with Smart Key System
‚Ä¢ Cold Weather Package with Heated Steering Wheel and Seats

Beyond the impressive powertrain and fuel economy, this Camry SE is outfitted with a host of premium amenities that cater to your every need. Enjoy the convenience of wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, the clarity of a 6-speaker audio system, and the added security of the Toyota Safety Sense suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies.

The sleek, modern exterior is complemented by the stunning 18" black-finished alloy wheels, while the interior is adorned with premium SofTex and fabric seating, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, and an illuminated trunk sill for a touch of elegance. With ample passenger and cargo space, this Camry SE is the perfect companion for your daily commute, weekend getaways, and everything in between.

Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2025 Toyota Camry SE. Combining performance, efficiency, and an impressive array of features, this sedan is poised to exceed your expectations and provide years of reliable, enjoyable driving. Visit our showroom today to experience it for yourself and discover why the Camry SE is the perfect choice for your next vehicle.

Call us now at (901)854-5337 or visit us at the corner of 385 and Byhalia in Collierville.

Elevate your driving experience with the 2025 Chevrolet Malibu LT 1LT. This exceptional sedan boasts a captivating Radiant Red Tintcoat exterior that commands attention wherever it goes. Beneath the striking design lies a refined and responsive 1.5L DOHC engine, paired with a smooth-shifting CVT transmission and front-wheel drive, delivering an exceptional balance of performance and efficiency.

Explore the standout features that set this Malibu apart:

Indulge in the comfort and convenience of this well-equipped LT 1LT model. The Preferred Equipment Group 1LT provides a host of desirable amenities, including a 6-speaker audio system, dual-zone automatic climate control, and an 8-way power driver's seat with lumbar support.

Safety is a top priority, with features like anti-lock brakes, electronic stability control, and a comprehensive airbag system to give you peace of mind on the road. The Malibu also boasts a rearview camera and OnStar emergency communication system, ensuring you're connected and protected.

With an EPA-estimated 28 mpg in the city and 36 mpg on the highway, this Malibu delivers exceptional fuel efficiency to help you go further on every tank. Whether commuting or embarking on a road trip, you'll enjoy the Malibu's blend of style, performance, and practicality.

This 2025 Chevrolet Malibu LT 1LT is available now at our dealership for just $20,580. We invite you to schedule a test drive and discover the exceptional value and driving experience this Malibu has to offer.

Discover the ultimate driving experience with this stunning 2023 INFINITI Q50 LUXE. Boasting a powerful 3.0L V6 engine, this certified pre-owned gem delivers an exceptional blend of performance and luxury.

Meticulously maintained and backed by a comprehensive 7-year/100,000-mile limited warranty, this Q50 LUXE is a true standout. Enjoy the peace of mind that comes with CARFAX certification, showcasing a clean vehicle history and no accidents. As a one-owner vehicle, you can trust that this Q50 has been well-cared for.

Slip behind the wheel and experience the Q50's exceptional handling and responsiveness, thanks to its rear-wheel-drive configuration and 7-speed automatic transmission with overdrive. With an impressive 29 MPG on the highway, this INFINITI will keep you moving efficiently, whether commuting or embarking on a road trip.

Indulge in the luxurious interior, featuring heated leather seats, a power moonroof, and a premium audio system with 16 speakers. The INFINITI InTouch Dual HD Display System keeps you connected and in control, while the Bluetooth hands-free calling and rear USB/power delivery port add to the vehicle's convenience.

Safety is paramount, and this Q50 LUXE delivers with a suite of advanced features, including a rear-view camera, blind spot warning, and electronic stability control. Rest assured, you and your passengers will be well-protected on the road.

Discover the exceptional value and uncompromising quality of this 2023 INFINITI Q50 LUXE. Schedule a test drive today and experience the difference for yourself. We're confident this certified pre-owned gem will exceed your expectations and become the perfect addition to your driving lifestyle.

Check out this 2023 Chevrolet Malibu LT finished in Mosaic Black Metallic with a Jet Black interior. This vehicle is equipped with the following features and options: Preferred Equipment Group 1LT
    Safety and Security
    • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
    • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
    • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
    • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Apple CarPlay/Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
    • Wireless Apple CarPlay/Wireless Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
    • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

Thank you for choosing Holler Honda, this Classic Silver Metallic 2023 Toyota Corolla LE is a great choice! Check out the following: No Accidents! One Owner! This Corolla has the following features: Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.

description:
Discover the Thrilling Performance and Sophisticated Style of the 2023 Kia K5 GT-Line

Prepare to be captivated by the exceptional 2023 Kia K5 GT-Line, a masterful blend of dynamic power, refined elegance, and cutting-edge technology. This stunning sedan is poised to elevate your driving experience, offering a level of sophistication and exhilaration that will leave you thoroughly impressed.

‚Ä¢ Navigation System
‚Ä¢ 6 Speakers
‚Ä¢ AM/FM radio: SiriusXM
‚Ä¢ Radio data system
‚Ä¢ Radio: AM/FM/MP3 Audio System
‚Ä¢ Air Conditioning
‚Ä¢ Automatic temperature control
‚Ä¢ Front dual zone A/C
‚Ä¢ Rear window defroster
‚Ä¢ Power driver seat
‚Ä¢ Power steering
‚Ä¢ Power windows
‚Ä¢ Remote keyless entry
‚Ä¢ Steering wheel mounted audio controls

Beneath its sleek and sophisticated exterior, the K5 GT-Line is powered by a turbocharged 1.6L I4 engine, delivering an impressive 180 horsepower and exceptional fuel efficiency with an EPA-estimated 27 city/37 highway MPG. This dynamic powertrain, paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission, ensures a thrilling and responsive driving experience that will leave you craving the open road.

The K5 GT-Line's striking design is a testament to Kia's commitment to craftsmanship and attention to detail. The bold, sculpted lines and striking 18-inch alloy wheels create a commanding presence on the road, while the available features such as auto high-beam headlights and front fog lights enhance both the vehicle's style and functionality.

Step inside the K5 GT-Line and you'll be greeted by a cabin that seamlessly blends premium materials and advanced technologies. The available leather-wrapped steering wheel and shift knob provide a tactile and refined driving experience, while the intuitive infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration keeps you connected and entertained.

Safety is of the utmost importance in the K5 GT-Line, which is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. Features like Forward Collision-Avoidance Assist, Lane Keeping Assist, and Blind Spot Monitoring work tirelessly to help keep you and your passengers secure on every journey.

Whether you're seeking a dynamic daily driver or a sophisticated weekend companion, the 2023 Kia K5 GT-Line is poised to exceed your expectations. Experience the thrill of the open road and the confidence of cutting-edge technology in this exceptional sedan. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why the K5 GT-Line should be your next automotive passion.

description:
Thank you for choosing Holler Honda, this Rallye Red 2023 Honda Civic Sport is a great choice! Check out the following: One Owner! RALLYE RED, BLACK, CLOTH SEAT TRIM This Civic has the following features: Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
At Holler Honda, all of our vehicles are clearly marked with our haggle-free best price and our sales associates are commission-free. That means they'll help you find the car that fits you best, not the one that earns them the biggest commission check. Every vehicle we sell comes with guaranteed peace of mind. Unhappy with your purchase? Take advantage of our market-leading return policy and bring it back within five days or three hundred miles, plain and simple. description:
This 2023 Toyota Corolla LE is a standout choice for the discerning driver seeking a compact sedan that seamlessly blends style, efficiency, and advanced technology. With its sleek black exterior and well-appointed interior, this Corolla LE exudes an air of sophistication and refinement.

Boasting an impressive array of features, this Corolla LE is equipped to enhance your driving experience. Key highlights include:

‚Ä¢ 6 Speakers
‚Ä¢ 8" Toyota Audio Multimedia System
‚Ä¢ Automatic Temperature Control
‚Ä¢ Keyless Entry
‚Ä¢ Steering Wheel Mounted Audio Controls
‚Ä¢ Traction Control
‚Ä¢ Dual Front Airbags and Side Impact Airbags
‚Ä¢ Rear View Camera
‚Ä¢ Auto High-Beam Headlights

The Corolla LE's 2.0L I4 DOHC 16V engine, paired with a CVT transmission and front-wheel drive, delivers an exceptional balance of power and efficiency, earning an EPA-estimated 32 city/41 highway MPG. This sedan's responsive handling and smooth ride quality make it a joy to drive, whether navigating city streets or cruising down the highway.

This 2023 Toyota Corolla LE has been meticulously inspected and certified to ensure it meets the highest standards of quality and reliability. You can have confidence in its performance and longevity, knowing that it has undergone a thorough evaluation and comes with the backing of Toyota's renowned reputation for excellence.

At the heart of the Corolla LE's appeal is its versatility. This compact sedan seamlessly blends practicality and style, making it an ideal choice for a wide range of drivers, from young professionals to growing families. With its spacious interior, ample cargo capacity, and advanced safety features, the Corolla LE is ready to accommodate your lifestyle with ease.

Experience the exceptional value and peace of mind that comes with owning this 2023 Toyota Corolla LE. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this remarkable vehicle can enhance your driving experience and exceed your expectations.

Powered by a 1.5L I4 DOHC 16V engine and equipped with a CVT transmission, the Integra A-Spec offers an exceptional balance of responsiveness and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 29 city/36 highway MPG. Its finely-tuned chassis and four-wheel independent suspension provide a thrilling yet refined driving experience, allowing you to tackle the open road with confidence and poise.

Elevating the driving experience further, the Integra A-Spec boasts a host of premium features designed to enhance your comfort and convenience. Enjoy the convenience of dual-zone automatic climate control, the versatility of a power driver's seat, and the connectivity of the Acura Premium Audio System with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration. The sleek, modern exterior is complemented by 18-inch alloy wheels and a sporty rear spoiler, giving the Integra A-Spec a bold and sophisticated presence.

Safety is paramount in the Integra A-Spec, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including Lane Keeping Assist, Collision Mitigation Braking, and Adaptive Cruise Control. These cutting-edge features work in harmony to help keep you and your passengers secure on the road.

Elevate your driving experience and make a statement with the 2023 Acura Integra A-Spec Package. Priced at just $25,803, this exceptional vehicle offers unparalleled value and a level of refinement that is truly unmatched in its class. Visit our showroom today to experience the Integra A-Spec for yourself and discover the true meaning of driving pleasure.

  • First Aid Kit
  • Shopping Bag Hooks
  • Cargo Net

Convenience
  • Distance pacing cruise control - Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with Distance pacing cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and the vehicle ahead. Distance pacing cruise control, your ultimate co-pilot.
  • Distance pacing cruise control - Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with Distance pacing cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and the vehicle ahead. Distance pacing cruise control, your ultimate co-pilot.
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
  • Keyfob engine start control - Get an early start. Remotely start your vehicle's engine from the key fob, ensuring your ride is ready to go when you get in. Now you can stay comfortable inside while your vehicle gets comfortable outside, thanks to Keyfob engine start control.
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Rear collision mitigation - It has your back. Rear collision mitigation uses sensors to monitor the area behind you. If it senses an impending crash, it activates certain features to help prevent a collision or reduce the severity of it. Put your worries behind you with rear collision mitigation.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Wireless Apple CarPlay/Wired Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

Boasting an impressive 138 MPGe in the city and 126 MPGe on the highway, the 2023 Tesla Model 3 Base delivers exceptional efficiency and performance, seamlessly blending power and sustainability. Its electric motor and single-speed transmission provide instant acceleration and a remarkably smooth, responsive ride, ensuring you'll enjoy every moment behind the wheel.

Step inside the spacious, well-appointed cabin and you'll be surrounded by a wealth of advanced features. The state-of-the-art infotainment system, complete with navigation, audio memory, and an upgraded sound system, keeps you connected and entertained. Dual-zone climate control, heated front seats, and a heated steering wheel provide exceptional comfort, while the power driver's seat and steering wheel memory settings allow you to personalize your driving experience.

With its powerful engine, spacious interior, and advanced safety features, you won't want to drive anything else. Upgrade to the E-Class E 450 4MATIC and elevate your driving experience to a whole new level.

Experience the Thrill of the Open Road in the 2019 Kia Stinger Base

Introducing the 2019 Kia Stinger Base, a captivating blend of style, performance, and cutting-edge technology. This dynamic sedan is ready to elevate your driving experience and turn heads wherever you go.

‚Ä¢ Sun & Sound Package
‚Ä¢ LED Headlights & Rear Turn Signals
‚Ä¢ Power Sunroof
‚Ä¢ 720-Watt harman/kardon Audio System
‚Ä¢ 8-Inch Color Touch-Screen Display
‚Ä¢ UVO eServices Infotainment System
‚Ä¢ Android Auto and Apple CarPlay Compatibility

Powered by a turbocharged 2.0-liter I4 engine, the Stinger Base delivers an exhilarating 255 horsepower and seamless 8-speed automatic transmission, all with the added confidence of Kia's advanced All-Wheel Drive system. Enjoy exceptional fuel efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 21 mpg in the city and 29 mpg on the highway.

Beyond its dynamic performance, the Stinger Base offers a wealth of premium features that elevate your driving experience. The Sun & Sound Package includes a power sunroof, LED headlights and rear turn signals, and a stunning 720-watt harman/kardon audio system with 15 speakers for an immersive listening experience.

The Stinger's interior is equally impressive, with luxurious leather seating, heated front seats, and a power driver's seat for maximum comfort. The 8-inch color touch-screen display puts cutting-edge technology at your fingertips, featuring the UVO eServices infotainment system, as well as seamless integration with Android Auto and Apple CarPlay.

Safety is also a top priority in the Stinger Base, with advanced features like forward collision warning, automatic emergency braking, and a rearview camera to give you peace of mind on every journey.

Whether you're seeking a thrilling daily commute or a weekend getaway companion, the 2019 Kia Stinger Base is the perfect choice. Experience the joy of driving with Kia's commitment to quality, style, and innovation. Visit our showroom today and let us help you discover the Stinger that's right for you.

Paired with the smooth-shifting 8-speed automatic transmission, this Camry SE delivers a responsive and engaging driving experience, whether you're navigating city streets or cruising the highway.

Inside, you'll find a wealth of premium features that elevate the driving experience, including a state-of-the-art navigation system, automatic climate control, and a premium audio system with Apple CarPlay. The sport-inspired front bucket seats and leather-wrapped steering wheel add a touch of sophistication, while the rear-view camera and advanced safety technologies, such as electronic stability control and traction control, provide added peace of mind.

With its impressive list of features, exceptional fuel economy, and sleek, modern styling, this 2019 Toyota Camry SE is a compelling choice for the discerning driver. Whether you're looking for a practical daily commuter or a versatile family sedan, this Camry SE is sure to impress.

The Lexus ES 300h hybrid version provides all the luxury but aims to save fuel with a gasoline/electric powertrain. Lexus and Toyota are credited with essentially inventing the modern hybrid and the ES utilizes that technology to its fullest, earning a combined EPA estimated 40 mpg. Interesting features of this model are Incredible chassis dynamics, hybrid efficiency, terrific interior room and comfort levels, and V6 power

This 2021 Toyota Camry SE Nightshade is a standout in the midsize sedan segment, blending style, technology, and performance in a sophisticated package. With its sleek black exterior accents and premium alloy wheels, this Camry commands attention on the road. But it's not just about good looks - this sedan is packed with an impressive array of features to elevate your driving experience.

Under the hood, you'll find a 2.5L I4 DOHC 16V engine mated to an 8-speed automatic transmission, delivering an exceptional balance of power and efficiency. With 28 MPG in the city and 39 MPG on the highway, this Camry will keep you moving without breaking the bank at the gas pump.

Step inside and you'll be greeted by a well-appointed cabin that seamlessly blends style and technology. Heated seats, Apple CarPlay, and Android Auto integration keep you comfortable and connected, while advanced safety features like Dynamic Radar Cruise Control, Lane Departure Alert, and Pre-Collision System provide added peace of mind on the road.

The SE Nightshade package takes this Camry to the next level, with sleek black accents that give it a bold, sporty appearance. From the black-painted alloy wheels to the black rear spoiler, this sedan exudes a sense of refined sophistication that is sure to turn heads.

Whether you're commuting to the office, running errands, or embarking on a road trip, this 2021 Toyota Camry SE Nightshade is the perfect companion. With its exceptional blend of style, technology, and performance, it's a midsize sedan that simply can't be beat.

Our Best Price! First Time, Every Time!
Our sales people understand that buying a new or used vehicle can be a stressful experience. After all, statistics show that, after a home, an automobile is the biggest investment most of us will ever make. And, with most car dealers you are forced to enter a haggling/negotiating game to TRY to get the best deal possible.

It's just too much!!
But that is not the case at Quality Toyota. Our commitment to Bottom Line Pricing means that you get Our Best Price the first time, every time. You get our best price even before you talk to a sales person because Our Best Price is posted in the window of every vehicle on our lot.

The No Hassle/No Haggle Way to Buy a Car, SUV, or Truck
The fact that it is unnecessary to spend a great deal of time negotiating means that our salespeople can place emphasis where it belongs, finding the best possible vehicle for you, based on your needs and budget. After we find that vehicle (which will already have Our Best Price), we can focus on ensuring that you are completely satisfied with your purchase. Our goal is to make the car buying experience as pleasant and stress-free as possible.

  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.

It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.

description: Experience the thrill of the road in this stunning 2021 Subaru WRX. Finished in the sleek and sophisticated Crystal Black Silica, this all-wheel-drive sedan is a true performance icon. You'll be settled into Performance Design Front Bucket Seats featuring Checkered Cloth Upholstery, providing the support you need for spirited driving. The Exterior Parking Camera Rear gives you a clear view when reversing, and the Auto-Dimming Mirror with Compass and HomeLink makes evening drives and arriving home a breeze. With features like Heated Door Mirrors, Remote Keyless Entry, and Electronic Stability Control, this Subaru is as practical for daily life as it is exciting for weekend adventures.This 2021 WRX is the perfect blend of rally-bred heritage and modern technology. Whether you're a long-time enthusiast or looking for your first performance vehicle, this Crystal Black sedan is ready to impress with its sharp handling and turbocharged power. description: Experience the future of driving with this stunning 2021 Polestar 2 Launch Edition. Dressed in a clean, crisp White exterior, this all-electric 4D Hatchback combines minimalist Scandinavian design with exhilarating performance. With its dual-motor All-Wheel Drive system, you get a smooth, quiet, and powerful ride that makes every trip feel special, whether you are commuting to work or heading out for a weekend adventure.Step inside and you will find a cabin that prioritizes both comfort and advanced technology. The interior features premium WeaveTech seating with Black Ash Deco accents, creating a modern and sustainable luxury feel. Stay cozy no matter the weather with heated front and rear seats, plus a heated steering wheel. The dual-zone automatic temperature control ensures everyone stays comfortable, while the massive panoramic feel of the cabin makes the space feel open and inviting.Technology is at the heart of the Polestar 2 experience. The harman kardon High Performance Pro audio system delivers crystal-clear sound through 13 high-end speakers, turning your car into a mobile concert hall. Navigating is a breeze with the integrated Navigation System, and the Exterior Parking Camera makes tucking into tight spots easier than ever. Plus, with features like a Power Liftgate and Remote Keyless Entry, your daily routine becomes much more convenient.Safety is never an afterthought in this Launch Edition. It comes loaded with smart driver-assist features including a Lane Departure Warning System, Auto High-beam Headlights, and a comprehensive airbag system to keep you and your passengers protected. The Rain Sensing Wipers and Auto-dimming mirrors adjust to your environment automatically, allowing you to stay focused on the road ahead.At the Superior Pre-Owned Superstore of Bentonville, we make the buying process simple and exciting. This Polestar 2 has been thoroughly cleaned, serviced, and is ready to make you smile the moment you get behind the wheel. We are here to answer all your questions, including "What is my trade worth?" Come see why our customers drive away feeling like they just bought a brand-new car! Visit us at http://www.bentonvillepreowned.com or call today to schedule your test drive.Faster. Simpler. More Transparent. Superior Automotive Group has helped thousands of customers find the right car by leveraging one of Arkansas' largest selections of new and pre-owned vehicles at unparalleled prices. Yet, it's our extra-mile customer service and uncommonly candid and respectful staff that have won the trust and loyalty of Arkansas drivers for 30 years. Come visit one of our Superior dealerships today and let us exceed your expectations.
