description:
The 2021 Honda Civic Sport is a remarkable vehicle that stands out with its dynamic performance and advanced safety features. This model comes equipped with an efficient 2L I-4 DOHC engine, utilizing i-VTEC variable valve control to produce an impressive 158HP paired with a CVT transmission. The Civic Sport is perfect for those who value both style and functionality on the road.

One of the most noteworthy aspects of the Civic Sport is its Smart Device Mirroring feature. This innovative technology allows you to connect your smartphone seamlessly to the vehicles infotainment system, enhancing convenience and safety. You can easily access vital functions while keeping your focus on the road ahead, making your driving experience more enjoyable.

Safety is a top priority for the Honda Civic Sport, exemplified by its advanced Forward Collision Mitigation system. This proactive technology continuously monitors the road ahead, preparing the vehicle for potential impacts and taking necessary actions to either avoid or mitigate the severity of a collision. Additionally, the Front Pedestrian Impact Prevention system actively tracks pedestrians, ensuring a safer environment for both drivers and pedestrians, particularly in urban settings.

Reversing is effortless with the Rear Camera, providing a clear view of any obstacles behind you, ensuring youre always aware of your surroundings. The Lane Departure Prevention system further enhances safety by automatically correcting any unintended lane drifts, helping you stay securely in your lane even during distractions.

For long highway drives, the Adaptive Cruise Control with Traffic Stop-Go feature is a game-changer. This system maintains your desired speed while adjusting to keep a safe distance from the vehicle ahead, even bringing your car to a stop if necessary when traffic halts. Coupled with Brake Assist, which enhances stopping power during emergencies, the Civic Sport is well-equipped to handle diverse driving conditions confidently.

The Cruise Control with Steering Wheel Mounted Controls enhances convenience, allowing you to effortlessly maintain speed and reduce fatigue during longer trips. With Keyfob Vehicle Start Control, you can remotely start your engine, ensuring your car is ready for you when you need it.

Finally, the user-friendly Touchscreen interface makes accessing features intuitive, letting you enjoy modern conveniences without distraction. In conclusion, the 2021 Honda Civic Sport is an outstanding choice for anyone seeking a harmonious blend of performance, safety, and cutting-edge technology.

description: This 2021 Genesis G70 3.3T in sophisticated Vik Black is the perfect blend of athletic performance and high-end luxury. Powered by a potent V6 engine and an 8-speed automatic transmission, this sedan offers a thrilling drive every time you hit the road. With its Clean CARFAX, you can be confident that this vehicle has been well-maintained and is ready to deliver an exceptional experience for its next owner.The interior is a true sanctuary, featuring Nappa Leather Seating Surfaces with beautiful quilting and a premium Microfiber Suede Headliner. You and your passengers will stay comfortable in any season thanks to Heated and Ventilated Front Seats, Heated Rear Seats, and a Heated Steering Wheel. The attention to detail is remarkable, right down to the Copper Headlight Bezel Accents and Dark Chrome trim that give this G70 a unique, aggressive edge.Tech-savvy drivers will love the advanced features packed into this sedan. The Heads-Up Display (HUD) keeps vital information in your line of sight, while the Navigation System and Surround View Monitor make every journey and parking maneuver effortless. You can enjoy your favorite playlist through the high-fidelity Lexicon Audio System, seamlessly connected via Apple CarPlay or Android Auto.Driving dynamics are enhanced by the Electronically Controlled Suspension and the Sport Package, ensuring a ride that is as smooth as it is responsive. Safety and convenience go hand-in-hand with features like Auto High-beam Headlights, Rain Sensing Wipers, and a Power Trunk. This car doesn't just get you where you're going, it makes sure you arrive in style and total comfort.At the Superior Pre-Owned Superstore of Bentonville, we make it our mission to provide a transparent and easy car-buying process. We've fully cleaned and serviced this Genesis to ensure it feels just like a brand-new car when you drive it home. Let us help you determine what your trade is worth and get you behind the wheel of this incredible machine today.Faster. Simpler. More Transparent. Superior Automotive Group has helped thousands of customers find the right car by leveraging one of Arkansas' largest selections of new and pre-owned vehicles at unparalleled prices. Yet, it's our extra-mile customer service and uncommonly candid and respectful staff that have won the trust and loyalty of Arkansas drivers for 30 years. Come visit one of our Superior dealerships today and let us exceed your expectations.

description:
Check out this recent arrival at Autobahn Volkswagen in Fort Worth, TX - a 2021 Nissan Sentra SR finished in the eye-catching Scarlet Ember Tintcoat. With sporty styling, advanced technology, and an efficient yet responsive powertrain, this Sentra SR delivers exceptional value for drivers looking for comfort, reliability, and modern features at a price they can feel great about.

This Sentra is powered by a 2.0L DOHC engine paired with a CVT with Xtronic, delivering smooth acceleration and impressive fuel efficiency for daily commuting or longer highway drives. With front-wheel drive and four-wheel independent suspension, the Sentra SR offers confident handling and a composed ride. The 18-inch alloy wheels, rear spoiler, and bold exterior accents give it a sport-inspired look that stands out wherever you go.

Inside, the cabin is thoughtfully designed with comfort and convenience in mind. The Sport Cloth or Prima-Tex seat trim, front bucket seats, and leather-wrapped shift knob create a refined, driver-focused environment. Dual-zone automatic climate control, power windows and mirrors, a tilt and telescoping steering wheel, and illuminated entry add everyday ease. The split-folding rear seat and trunk mat provide added versatility for cargo and travel needs.

Technology is a highlight in this Sentra SR. Stay connected with NissanConnect featuring Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, SiriusXM capability, and a 6-speaker audio system. Steering-wheel-mounted audio controls, Bluetooth connectivity, and a trip computer help keep everything within easy reach while you stay focused on the road.

Safety and driver-assistance features are abundant, offering peace of mind on every drive. This vehicle includes Blind Spot Warning, Rear Parking Sensors, Automatic High-Beam Headlights, Electronic Stability Control, Traction Control, Brake Assist, and a full suite of airbags, including knee and side-impact airbags. Additional features such as a rear window defroster, security system, panic alarm, and tire pressure monitoring system further enhance confidence behind the wheel.

This 2021 Nissan Sentra SR has 55,510 miles on the odometer and carried an original MSRP of $23,360. It has recently arrived and is available now at Autobahn Volkswagen. We use market-based pricing, so you can be confident this Sentra is priced competitively within current market conditions. With a wide variety of vehicles available, including several pre-owned Volkswagen and Audi models, finding the right vehicle for your lifestyle is easy at our Fort Worth dealership.

For added peace of mind, extended service contracts are available on this vehicle. Autobahn Volkswagen also offers nationwide delivery, making it simple to purchase from anywhere. Can't make it to the dealership right away? Ask your sales associate for a virtual walkaround and see this Sentra SR up close from the comfort of your own home.

Visit Autobahn Volkswagen in Fort Worth, TX, today and discover how easy and enjoyable your next vehicle purchase can be.
